<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>We received a request to reset your password for your {{=it.appName}} account.</p>

{{? it.resetLink}}
<p>Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{=it.resetLink}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
</div>
<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;">
  Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
  <a href="{{=it.resetLink}}" style="color: #0ea5e9;">{{=it.resetLink}}</a>
</p>
{{?}}

{{? it.expiresAt}}
<div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #fef9c3; border-left: 4px solid #eab308; color: #854d0e; font-size: 14px;">
  <strong>Note:</strong> This link will expire on {{=it.expiresAt}}.
</div>
{{?}}

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8;">If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
